    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入我们的社区</h2><strong>QQ群: 812627126</strong><br><strong>B站: </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器好几种</h2>目前提供了5种武器可供使用，它们分别是，弓，枪，炮，斧，琴。后续还会增加更多武器变种。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158380/extras/武器好几种s.gif?t=1695030478\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大坐快乐多</h2>黄游中独特的、快节奏的、大坐系统，越坐越快乐。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158380/extras/操作花样多s.gif?t=1695030478\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长很丰富</h2>在游戏中有大量的道具和技能，通过不同的搭配，形成不同的战斗风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158380/extras/道具一大堆s.gif?t=1695030478\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人炸了窝</h2>在不同的场景，会遭遇不同的敌人，它们形态各异，性格多样，劈里啪啦，咔咔冒水。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158380/extras/敌人炸了窝s.gif?t=1695030478\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3A级游戏体验</h2>虽然这只是一个小团队的独立游戏，但我们希望营造出3A级的游戏体验，而令人愉快的是，我们做到了，我们成功的修改了3A的定义：A LOT OF 饼；A LOT OF 钱；A LOT OF 鱼。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158380/extras/3A级游玩体验s.gif?t=1695030478\" /></span>",
